task.summary: Can now handle N columns in a brick layout instead of a forced-height responsive row layout.
Ion-row needed to be in an ion-grid in order for nowrap to work.
Dramatically simplified html markup - columns now dynamic 1-4 based on real estate. Untested on devices though.
seamless infinite scrolling in the brick layout. Ionic's virtual scroll only works for list, and is thus absolutely useless to me.
